<template>
    <button class="btn" :class="[`btn-${type}`, `btn-${size}`]">
      {{ label }}
    </button>
  </template>
  
  <script>
  export default {
    props: {
      label: String,
      type: {
        validator(value) {
          return [
            "primary",
            "outline-primary",
            "link",
            "tertiary",
            "secondary",
          ].includes(value);
        },
      },
      size: {
        validator(value) {
          return ["sm", "md", "lg", "xl"].includes(value);
        },
      },
    },
  };
  </script>
